# --- Contact form delivery -------------------------------------------------
# The form at /contact needs ONE of these to actually reach an inbox.
# With neither set, the form refuses to pretend: it tells the visitor the
# message was NOT sent and shows the mailto address instead.

# Option A (recommended, zero setup, works with a plain Gmail address):
# Get a free access key at https://web3forms.com — enter tenzok.tech@gmail.com,
# they email you the key. Submissions are relayed through Web3Forms' servers.
WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=

# Option B (requires a verified sending domain at resend.com):
RESEND_API_KEY=
RESEND_FROM="Tenzok <hello@tenzok.tech>"
